{
  "texts": [
    "\"Why are you sitting here all by yourself?\"",
    "Jonah hesitated, unsure how to respond.",
    "How could he explain his complicated emotions to a child?",
    "\"I'm just thinking about the city,\" he said finally.",
    "\"I prophesied that it would be destroyed, but instead, the people repented and turned to God.\""
  ]
}